.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/14\/fudayl-nashihah-more-than-self\/","url_meta":{"origin":24319,"position":0},"title":"Fudayl on Sincerity: Good will to love others more than yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 14, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Asakir reported: Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf you love for people to be equal to you, you have not fulfilled sincerity for the sake of your Lord. How so while you love for people to be less than you?\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 48\/418\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21077,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/21\/fudayl-on-faith-nasihah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24319,"position":1},"title":"Fudayl on Faith: Believer is happy for others, has good will","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 21, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Fudayl ibn 'Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAdmiration is part of faith and envy is part of hypocrisy. The believer admires others and does not envy others. The hypocrite envies others and does not admire others. The believer overlooks the faults of others, admonishes\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19696,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/08\/05\/fudayl-on-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24319,"position":2},"title":"Fudayl on Sunnah: Deeds accepted if sincere and according to Sunnah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: Fudayl ibn 'Iyad said, \u201cAllah purifies good deeds and makes them correct. Indeed, if deeds are sincere and incorrect, they will not be accepted. If deeds are correct and insincere, they will not be accepted, but rather they are only accepted if they are both sincere and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34525,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/27\/iman-honest-innocent\/","url_meta":{"origin":24319,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Believers are honest, sinners are treacherous","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believer is naively generous, and the wicked one is deceitfully malicious.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1964 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064f \u063a\u0650\u0631\u0651\u064c \u0643\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064c\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27151,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/02\/07\/prophets-righteous-pure-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":24319,"position":4},"title":"Fudayl on Tazkiyyah: Prophets and righteous have pure hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIt has been said that among the character of the prophets and chosen elect is the purity of their hearts. They are three characteristics: forbearance, penitence, and a portion of prayer in the night.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304'\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24401,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/07\/nasihah-ikhlaas-hiqd\/","url_meta":{"origin":24319,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sincerity: Good will protects from hatred, malice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 7, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are three traits by which a believer will have no malice: sincerity in deeds for Allah, goodwill to the Muslims, and uniting with their community.\" Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 1279 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi\u00a0(authentic\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousn